title: Encyclopedia of Artists of the American West
description:
The Illustrated Biographical Encyclopedia of Artists of the American West
Doubleday & Company | 1976 | ISBN 0385017308 | Eng | 668 pages | PDF | 90 MB

A massive, informative, and the most comprehensive reference work on Western American Art ever published. This volume features over 1,700 concise and detailed biographies of painters, illustrators, and sculptors who fell under the spell of the American West
